Formula	Explanation
tr:nth-of-type(n)	Selects all table rows.
tr:nth-of-type(n+2)	Selects all table rows except
the first row (starting with the second row).
tr:nth-of-type(2n)	Selects every second row of the table.
tr:nth-of-type(3n)	Selects every third row of the table.
tr:nth-of-type(2n+4)	Selects every other row of the table,
starting with the fourth row.
td:nth-of-type(2)	Selects the second column.
td:nth-of-type(2n)	Selects every second column of the table.
td:nth-of-type(-n+3)	Selects first three columns of the table.
